{"tid":1435323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[續]試下用水魔法？有咩好處先？？？","createTime":"2019-08-09T04:20:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T04:49:42.000Z","uid":261627,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"73f226f3a13723f5754c0d6a5bfb5bb1916335a8","tid":1435323,"uid":261627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:20:10.000Z","msg":"點解唔開發新技能用水，對popo傷害好大<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1435022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1435022</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n見上一個po咁多人支持， 睇完下面啲留言，做啲歸納先<br />\n1）加咩都得， 大家創意無限我喺度講都講唔曬<br />\n2）可樂加萬樂珠<br />\n3）可攻擊(濕，笠，臭)，可防禦(跌)<br />\n4）濕膠袋自帶跣既效果<br />\n5）水攻係辛苦死佢地，無孔不入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n解決技術性問題<br />\n1）射程: 我哋依家有大彈弓, 但係其實就算掉得唔遠都唔怕, <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>佢地前面成地都係不明液體包括油，梘同埋爆咗嘅膠袋, 跣都跣死</strong></span>，最梗要夠多<br />\n<br />\n2）水:依家打地區戰，水喉水供應多咗， 不過都會有運上前線嘅問題， <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>可能要用黃白藍膠袋或者街市車嗰啲先運到大量， 但係回歸返原始方法， 用人鏈逐隻逐隻保鮮袋水彈咁運都可以</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n3）唔識爆: 有冇人試過用媽媽喺超市買生果嗰隻保鮮袋(非密實袋)？ 我諗應該會容易啲爆？ 但係都係嗰句， 就算唔易爆都好， 佢哋身邊周圍都係水彈， 就好似你細細個落咗波波池一樣， 仲要呢啲<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">水彈係一踩就爆， 一係就踩落去踩波車仆街</span></span><br />\n<br />\n4）輿論: 大家都擔心會俾人屈係腐蝕性液體， 但係我哋用嘅係保鮮袋， 我覺得由佢點講都冇所謂， 即使佢係話有害嘅不明液體， 一定唔夠其他攻擊物品咁強輿論，加上大家有 laser gun一事加持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，火又出咗，水攻又唔見血<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Btw, 得個講字係冇用, 希望見到有工廠妹/仔會一齊試，現場整完大量， 利用物資鏈運上前線， 再畀前線決定用唔用</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n仲有冇 brainstorm？？？<br />\n<br />\n唔係話唔用舊招， 只不過係想加啲新嘢試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee726dc63ed73e9fbfbf25be335bba905cc4f162","tid":1435323,"uid":277513,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:23:10.000Z","msg":"直接用磁七彈啦，好難洗嫁"},{"pid":"08bc57b38affbf0f7e60e19ade4bb8bc57a62362","tid":1435323,"uid":261627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:27:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d659ba8a7bda5edde901e18aea2970f34ca82a71","tid":1435323,"uid":261627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb9c241330624e1f14630ea81689b7b947b2c84","tid":1435323,"uid":261627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:27:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7565d8948e27f15c65b6e8a127dbd77a9966221","tid":1435323,"uid":261627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:28:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efc168cd4444a611ca0d1884cccfb37cf3b35a74","tid":1435323,"uid":261627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:28:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"531e2e423cc836b97b936b5e169741c4f5e1f78a","tid":1435323,"uid":261627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:28:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf81d3a51a59c496a46950b19191c7362c73f10","tid":1435323,"uid":261627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:28:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"202c43ad49f5f221aa6fc53353006cb5db18c28f","tid":1435323,"uid":88428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:29:03.000Z","msg":"覺得有用 推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勇武是要對警/黑社會<br />\n<br />\n政府唔係民意授權<br />\n捆綁大眾民生同政府角力毫無意思<br />\n所以阻人上機個兩三日冇意思<br />\n<br />\n但接機係有用 因為可以宣揚<br />\nHong Kong is China already<br />\nStop trading with Hong Kong <br />\