replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:37:14.000Z","msg":"［神器開箱］八月就到，又係Ocamp水戰嘅時候<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1387135\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1387135</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2ff6d5a5c95cfc8f8290b35f964e5593cc9d7e49","tid":1435323,"uid":82359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a01985bae432b06add3c2cb023be73dd6a3abef","tid":1435323,"uid":302831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:36:15.000Z","msg":"雞蛋係咩系魔法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:38:15.000Z","msg":"可能係召喚魔法，不過失敗咗"},{"pid":"ed57203aba1d077fd2ae852f8057f3c894f4f8f9","tid":1435323,"uid":2036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4878f3b8026772b4a0fe9780718a7ffae7e66168","tid":1435323,"uid":184379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:33:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:38:33.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"512b2b98662bc914e3a6e63e4836768effda7090","tid":1435323,"uid":173577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"73f226f3a13723f5754c0d6a5bfb5bb1916335a8","tid":1435323,"uid":261627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:20:10.000Z","msg":"點解唔開發新技能用水，對popo傷害好大<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1435022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1435022</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n見上一個po咁多人支持， 睇完下面啲留言，做啲歸納先<br />\n1）加咩都得， 大家創意無限我喺度講都講唔曬<br />\n2）可樂加萬樂珠<br />\n3）可攻擊(濕，笠，臭)，可防禦(跌)<br />\n4）濕膠袋自帶跣既效果<br />\n5）水攻係辛苦死佢地，無孔不入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n解決技術性問題<br />\n1）射程: 我哋依家有大彈弓, 但係其實就算掉得唔遠都唔怕, <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>佢地前面成地都係不明液體包括油，梘同埋爆咗嘅膠袋, 跣都跣死</strong></span>，最梗要夠多<br />\n<br />\n2）水:依家打地區戰，水喉水供應多咗， 不過都會有運上前線嘅問題， <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>可能要用黃白藍膠袋或者街市車嗰啲先運到大量， 但係回歸返原始方法， 用人鏈逐隻逐隻保鮮袋水彈咁運都可以</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n3）唔識爆: 有冇人試過用媽媽喺超市買生果嗰隻保鮮袋(非密實袋)？ 我諗應該會容易啲爆？ 但係都係嗰句， 就算唔易爆都好， 佢哋身邊周圍都係水彈， 就好似你細細個落咗波波池一樣， 仲要呢啲<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">水彈係一踩就爆， 一係就踩落去踩波車仆街</span></span><br />\n<br />\n4）輿論: 大家都擔心會俾人屈係腐蝕性液體， 但係我哋用嘅係保鮮袋， 我覺得由佢點講都冇所謂， 即使佢係話有害嘅不明液體， 一定唔夠其他攻擊物品咁強輿論，加上大家有 laser gun一事加持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，火又出咗，水攻又唔見血<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Btw, 得個講字係冇用, 希望見到有工廠妹/仔會一齊試，現場整完大量， 利用物資鏈運上前線， 再畀前線決定用唔用</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n仲有冇 brainstorm？？？<br />\n<br />\n唔係話唔用舊招， 只不過係想加啲新嘢試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:43:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你要做水系魔法師，建議學以下技能</span>：<br />\n<br />\n1, <span style=\"color: violet;\">【水油定身術】 控制系魔法</span><br />\n<br />\n2, <span style=\"color: violet;\">【高蝕水龍彈】 群體攻擊魔法</span><br />\n<br />\n3,<span style=\"color: violet;\">【液態元素表】 水系最高技能</span></strong>"},{"pid":"32bff5cbbb241c71c41c81c7727eb68cf85bc892","tid":1435323,"uid":2036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:43:35.000Z","msg":"咁貴既, 街市有無D 散裝好似D 米鋪咁一斤斤稱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd46d990d0bf7c188722d2542cfffab0685961e4","tid":1435323,"uid":261627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb14096a0efbd01f20db8b18b7fc769060fbe56d","tid":1435323,"uid":293698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"60310d70a078488f1573d6f5eae5013924090b6a","tid":1435323,"uid":261627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c13e4c9ed41f823a9f30ac07606bfbbdfa6ae1f6","tid":1435323,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike